nodes.title: Tex Encoder (Prompt)
widgets_values: A colossal, ancient temple complex is carved into the rocky cliffs of a secluded, mist-laden valley, featuring grand arches, towering columns, and intricate stone facades adorned with faded frescoes and mosaics that depict mythical scenes and celestial maps. The architecture blends elements of Greco-Roman and Byzantine styles, evoking a sense of timelessness and reverence. A lone scholar, draped in dark, flowing robes reminiscent of monastic scribes, moves deliberately through the temple, their presence adding to the sceneâ€™s quiet, contemplative atmosphere. Soft, ethereal light filters through natural fissures in the rock, casting a muted glow that emphasizes the grandeur and mystery of the space. The geography suggests a remote, ancient land, far removed from civilization, with dense fog and towering cliffs enhancing the sense of seclusion and sacredness. The few figures present interact minimally, absorbed in their own silent quests for knowledge, adding to the overall feeling of introspection and awe as they navigate this vast, sacred sanctuary. Bokeh
